@startuml Admin_User_Management
title Admin User Management Sequence Diagram

actor Admin
participant "Frontend" as FE
participant "API Gateway" as API
participant "Admin Controller" as Ctrl
database "Database" as DB
participant "Security Log" as Log

== View Users ==
Admin -> FE: View User List
FE -> API: GET /admin/users
API -> Ctrl: Check Admin Role
Ctrl -> DB: Fetch All Users
Ctrl --> API: User List

== Deactivate User ==
Admin -> FE: Deactivate User
FE -> API: PUT /admin/users/{id}/deactivate
API -> Ctrl: Check Admin Role
Ctrl -> DB: Set isActive = false
Ctrl -> Log: Log Deactivation
Ctrl --> API: Success

== Delete User ==
Admin -> FE: Delete User
FE -> API: DELETE /admin/users/{id}
API -> Ctrl: Check Admin Role
Ctrl -> DB: Remove User & Data
Ctrl -> Log: Log User Deletion
Ctrl --> API: Success

@enduml
